import React from 'react';

function TableHeader() {
  return (
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Date</th>
        <th>Time of Drop</th>
        <th>Stake Size</th>
        <th>Sport</th>
        <th>Match</th>
        <th>Selection</th>
        <th>Odds</th>
        <th>Bookie</th>
        <th>Result</th>
        <th>Unit P/L</th>
        <th>P/L</th>
        <th>Rolling Profit</th>
        <th>Cumulative Stake</th>
        <th>Rolling ROI</th>
        <th>% Win</th>
        <th>Comments/Verification</th>
        <th>OC Link</th>
        <th>Rolling Unit Profit</th>
        <th>Cumulative Stake</th>
        <th>Rolling Unit ROI</th>
        <th>ROI Diff</th>
        <th>W/L</th>
        <th>N/V Bet</th>
        <th>Rolling W/L</th>
        <th>Rolling N/V Bet</th>
        <th>SR</th>
        <th>Rolling EX Win</th>
        <th>Diff</th>
        <th>Sum EX Win</th>
        <th>Sum Wins</th>
        <th>EX Win Diff</th>
        <th>AB</th>
        <th>Target Profit @5%</th>
        <th>Cum Target Profit @ 5%</th>
        <th>Target vs Actual</th>
        <th>Ave Win</th>
        <th>Ave Loss</th>
        <th>Pot Win</th>
        <th>Pot Loss</th>
        <th>100-MA</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
  );
}

export default TableHeader;
